Empath::

Before Proto has even drawn a bead, Empath is elsewhere.  Her mind-
reading ability lets her know exactly what her foe is about to do, 
hence her seemingly extraordinary reaction time.  She fires four 
bursts from each of her plasma blasters at the shapeshifter.  "Too 
predictable, honey," she admonishes.  "I already know just about 
every trick the Autobots and Decepticons have up their assorted metal 
sleeves - especially the famous ones."
